├── docs/                – GDPR authorities, domain WHOIS, API collection
├── LICENSE              – GPL-3.0 + additional terms
└── README.md            – this file
```

---

📊 Validator Income Data

The dashboard includes full historical income data (daily records from Sep 2023 to Dec 2020) for a real validator, demonstrating the platform’s capability. You can replace it with your own validator data via the API or CSV import.

